trans-unit.source: Represents the event arguments class for the <see cref="E:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IMenuItem.Click" /> event.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="E:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IMenuItem.Click" /> 事件的事件参数类。

trans-unit.source: The instance of Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IMenuItem that raises the event.
trans-unit.target: 引发事件的 Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IMenuItem 的实例。

trans-unit.source: An object that owns the menu item.
Typically this is a node visible in the UI such as a Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem or Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Explorer.IExplorerNode.
trans-unit.target: 通常这是在 UI 中显示的节点，如 Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem 或 Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Explorer.IExplorerNode。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.MenuItemEventArgs" /> class with the old value for the deployment type.
trans-unit.target: 使用部署类型的旧值初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.MenuItemEventArgs" /> 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: Gets an instance of <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IMenuItem" /> that raises the event.
trans-unit.target: 获取引发事件的 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IMenuItem" /> 的实例。

trans-unit.source: An object representing a menu item.
Gets the owner of the menu item.

Typically, this is a node visible in the UI such as an <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> or <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Explorer.IExplorerNode" />.
trans-unit.target: 通常这是在 UI 中显示的节点，例如 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.ISharePointProjectItem" /> 或 <see cref="T:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.Explorer.IExplorerNode" />。

trans-unit.source: An object representing the menu item owner.
trans-unit.target: 表示菜单项所有者的对象。
